    "html_format": "<div class=\"document-view-wrapper\">\n<style>\n.html-preview * {font-family: Times New Roman; font-size: 12pt;}\n.html-preview a.NoteRef {text-decoration: none;}\n.html-preview table td {vertical-align: top;}\n.html-preview table {width: 100%;}\n.html-preview p {white-space: pre-wrap;}\n.html-preview .leading {width: 4px; display: inline-block;}\n.html-preview hr {height: 1px; padding: 0; margin: 1em 0; border: 0; border-top: 1px solid #CCC;}\n.html-preview .a {font-size: 12pt;}\n.html-preview .a3 {font-family: 'Batang'; font-size: 14pt; font-weight: bold; font-style: italic;}\n.html-preview .a4 {font-family: 'Batang'; font-size: 14pt; font-weight: bold; font-style: italic;}\n.html-preview .customClass1 {font-family: 'Calibri'; font-size: 11pt;}\n.html-preview .NoSpacingChar1 {font-family: 'Calibri'; font-size: 11pt;}\n.html-preview .a5 td {border: 1px solid #000;}\n.html-preview .a6 {font-family: 'Batang'; font-size: 14pt;}\n.html-preview .a7 {font-family: 'Batang'; font-size: 14pt;}\n.html-preview .customClass10 {font-family: 'Batang'; font-size: 14pt;}\n</style>\n<div class=\"html-preview\">\n<style>.html-preview{width: 762px}</style><style>.html-preview{margin-top: 76px}</style><style>.html-preview{margin-bottom: 32px}</style><style>.html-preview{padding-left: 81px}</style><style>.html-preview{padding-right: 57px}</style><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold;\">ДАЛОЛАТНОМА</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">(Меҳнат дафтарчаларини йўқ қилиш тўғрисида)</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center; text-indent: 47.2px;\"><span class=\"structures structure-2\" style=\"\">{#2}Далолатнома тузилган сана</span><span class=\"tab\" style=\"width: 47.2px; display: inline-block\"></span> <span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"structures structure-3\" style=\"\">{#3}Далолатнома тузилган жой номи</span></p>\n<p></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 45.6px;\">Мазкур далолатнома <span class=\"structures structure-7\" style=\"\">{#7}Меҳнат дафтарчаларни йўқ қилаётган ташкилотнинг номи ва уни ташкилий ҳуқуқий шакли</span> <span class=\"structures structure-8\" style=\"\">{#8}Меҳнат дафтарчаларини йўқ қилиш тўғрисида буйруқ чиқарган шахснинг лавозими</span>нинг <span class=\"structures structure-10\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#10}Меҳнат дафтарчаларини йўқ қилиш тўғрисида буйруқ чиқарилган сана</span> кунидаги <span class=\"structures structure-11\" style=\"\">{#11}Буйруқ рақами</span>-сонли буйруғига мувофиқ Меҳнат дафтарчаларини йўқ қилиш бўйича вақтинчалик комиссия томонидан ташкилот архивида <span class=\"structures structure-12\" style=\"\">{#12}Меҳнат дафтарчалари архивда сақланган йили</span> - йилдан ортиқ муддат давомида сақланган <span class=\"structures structure-13\" style=\"\">{#13}Йўқ қилиниши лозим бўлган меҳнат дафтарчаларининг сони</span> дона меҳнат дафтарчаларини йўқ қилиш мақсадида тузилди.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 47.2px;\">Меҳнат дафтарчаларини йўқ қилинишига қонуний асос: Адлия вазирлиги томонидан 1998-йил 29-январда 402-сон билан давлат рўйхатидан ўтказилган “Меҳнат дафтарчаларини юритиш тартиби тўғрисида”ги Йўриқноманинг 5.2-банди.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 47.2px;\">Комиссия томонидан архивда сақланаётган ва йўқ қилиниши лозим бўлган қуйидаги меҳнат дафтарчалари аниқланди:</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 47.2px;\"></p>\n<table style=\"border: 1px solid; border-spacing: 0; \">\n<tr>\n<td 0=\"\" style=\"border: 1px solid #000; width: 38.825484764543px;\">\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">№</span></p>\n</td>\n<td 0=\"\" style=\"border: 1px solid #000; width: 190.47091412742px;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Меҳнат дафтарчаси эгаси (Ф.И.О)</span></p>\n</td>\n<td 0=\"\" style=\"border: 1px solid #000; width: 226.37119113573px;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Меҳнат дафтарчасининг серияси ва рақами</span></p>\n</td>\n<td 0=\"\" style=\"border: 1px solid #000; width: 173.45152354571px;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Архивда сақланган </span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">муддати</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td 1=\"\" style=\"border: 1px solid #000; width: 38.825484764543px;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">1</p>\n</td>\n<td 1=\"\" style=\"border: 1px solid #000; width: 190.47091412742px;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p>\n</td>\n<td 1=\"\" style=\"border: 1px solid #000; width: 226.37119113573px;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p>\n</td>\n<td 1=\"\" style=\"border: 1px solid #000; width: 173.45152354571px;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td 2=\"\" style=\"border: 1px solid #000; width: 38.825484764543px;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">2</p>\n</td>\n<td 2=\"\" style=\"border: 1px solid #000; width: 190.47091412742px;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p>\n</td>\n<td 2=\"\" style=\"border: 1px solid #000; width: 226.37119113573px;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p>\n</td>\n<td 2=\"\" style=\"border: 1px solid #000; width: 173.45152354571px;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td 3=\"\" style=\"border: 1px solid #000; width: 38.825484764543px;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">3</p>\n</td>\n<td 3=\"\" style=\"border: 1px solid #000; width: 190.47091412742px;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p>\n</td>\n<td 3=\"\" style=\"border: 1px solid #000; width: 226.37119113573px;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p>\n</td>\n<td 3=\"\" style=\"border: 1px solid #000; width: 173.45152354571px;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td 4=\"\" style=\"border: 1px solid #000; width: 38.825484764543px;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">4</p>\n</td>\n<td 4=\"\" style=\"border: 1px solid #000; width: 190.47091412742px;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p>\n</td>\n<td 4=\"\" style=\"border: 1px solid #000; width: 226.37119113573px;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p>\n</td>\n<td 4=\"\" style=\"border: 1px solid #000; width: 173.45152354571px;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td 5=\"\" style=\"border: 1px solid #000; width: 38.825484764543px;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">5</p>\n</td>\n<td 5=\"\" style=\"border: 1px solid #000; width: 190.47091412742px;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p>\n</td>\n<td 5=\"\" style=\"border: 1px solid #000; width: 226.37119113573px;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p>\n</td>\n<td 5=\"\" style=\"border: 1px solid #000; width: 173.45152354571px;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin-top: 2pt; margin-bottom: 2pt; text-indent: 47.2px;\"></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin-top: 2pt; margin-bottom: 2pt; text-indent: 47.2px;\">Комиссия томонидан <span class=\"structures structure-7\" style=\"\">{#7}Меҳнат дафтарчаларни йўқ қилаётган ташкилотнинг номи ва уни ташкилий ҳуқуқий шакли</span>нинг <span class=\"structures structure-14\" style=\"\">{#14}Меҳнат дафтарчалари йўқ қилинган жой</span> ҳудудида жами <span class=\"structures structure-13\" style=\"\">{#13}Йўқ қилиниши лозим бўлган меҳнат дафтарчаларининг сони</span> дона меҳнат дафтарчалари <span class=\"structures structure-15\" style=\"\">{#15}Меҳнат дафтарчаларининг йўқ қилиш усули</span> йўли билан йўқ қилинди ҳамда буни Комиссиянинг жами <span class=\"structures structure-16\" style=\"\">{#16}Жараёнда қатнашган комиссия аъзолари сони</span> нафар аъзоси тўлиқ тасдиқлади.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin-top: 2pt; margin-bottom: 2pt; text-indent: 47.2px;\">Меҳнат дафтарчаларини йўқ қилиш бўйича аниқ вақт: <span class=\"structures structure-17\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#17}Меҳнат дафтарчалари йўқ қилинган санаси </span> йил, соат: <span class=\"structures structure-18\" style=\"\">{#18}Меҳнат дафтарчалари йўқ қилинган соат</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin-top: 2pt; margin-bottom: 2pt; text-indent: 47.2px;\">Далолатома <span class=\"structures structure-19\" style=\"\">{#19}Далолатноманинг тузилган нусхаси сони</span> нусхада тузилди, <span class=\"structures structure-20\" style=\"\">{#20}Далолатнома сақлаш учун берилган бўлим номи</span>га<span style=\"color: #00b050;\"> </span>топширилди.</p>\n<p></p>\n<p></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin-top: 2pt; margin-bottom: 2pt;\">Далолатнома Комиссиянинг қуйидаги аъзолари томонидан имзоланди:</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin-top: 2pt; margin-bottom: 2pt;\"></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin-top: 2pt; margin-bottom: 2pt;\"><span class=\"structures structure-5\" style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">{#5}Имзолаётган шахснинг лавозими </span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"> <span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span></span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold;\"> <span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span></span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"> </span><span class=\"structures structure-6\" sty